title: Josef Suk: Epilogue - CzPO, Neumann (1989)
description:
JOSEF SUK (1874-1935)
Epilogue
Symphonic piece for orchestra, large and small mixed choruses, soprano, baritone and bass, Op. 37

1. Kroky / Footsteps (Adagio) att. [11:21]
2. Píseň matek / Mothers' Song (Andante semplice) att. [6:00]
3. Od věčnosti do věčnosti / From Eternity to Eternity (Allegro appassionato) att. [5:49]
4. Tajemný úžas a neklid / Mysterious Amazement and Agitation (Adagio maestoso e mesto) att. [3:52]
5. Poutník — těšitel / Pilgrim — Bringer of Consolation (Adagio molto tranquillo) [11:58]
Total time: 40:31

Zora Jehličková, soprano
Ivan Kusnjer, baritone
Ján Galla, bass
Czech Philharmonic Chorus (Lubomír Mátl: chorus master)
Czech Philharmonic Orchestra
Václav Neumann
